      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Computer and Games 2000</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/CG_1998\" title=\"CG 1998\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/CG_2002\" title=\"CG 2002\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p><p>The <b>Second International Conference on Computers and Games</b> was held in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamamatsu,_Shizuoka\">Hamamatsu</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Japan\">Japan</a>, October 26-28, <a href=\"/Timeline#2000\" title=\"Timeline\">2000</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Proceedings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Proceedings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Lectures\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lectures</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search_and_Strategies\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search and Strategies</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Learning_and_Pattern_Acquisition\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Learning and Pattern Acquisition</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Theory_and_Complexity_Issues\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Theory and Complexity Issues</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Further_Experiments_with_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Further Experiments with Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Invited_Talks_and_Reviews\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Invited Talks and Reviews</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Reports_.26_Reviews\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Reports &amp; Reviews</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Proceedings\">Proceedings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2000&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Proceedings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a> and <a href=\"/Ian_Frank\" title=\"Ian Frank\">Ian Frank</a> (eds.)</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/3-540-45579-5\">Computers and Games</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></dd>\n<dd> Second International Conference, CG 2000</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamamatsu,_Shizuoka\">Hamamatsu</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Japan\">Japan</a>, October 26 - 28, 2000</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lecture_Notes_in_Computer_Science\">Lecture Notes in Computer Science</a>, Volume 2063, 2001</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></dd>\n<dd> ISBN 3-540-43080-6 </dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lectures\">Lectures</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2000&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Lectures\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search_and_Strategies\">Search and Strategies</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2000&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search and Strategies\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Paul_E._Utgoff\" title=\"Paul E. Utgoff\">Paul E. Utgoff</a>, <a href=\"/Richard_P._Cochran\" title=\"Richard P. Cochran\">Richard P. Cochran</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_1\">A Least-Certainty Heuristic for Selective Search</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Richard_P._Cochran#LCF\" title=\"Richard P. Cochran\">LCF</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Thomsen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Thomas Thomsen (page does not exist)\">Thomas Thomsen</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_2\">Lambda-Search in Game Trees - with Application to Go</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a> also published in <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#23_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 23, No. 4</a>, winning the 2001 <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#JournalAward\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal Award</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.t-t.dk/publications/lambda_icga.pdf\">preprint as pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lambda-Search&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lambda-Search (page does not exist)\">Lambda-Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_3\">Abstract Proof Search</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lamsade.dauphine.fr/~cazenave/papers/APS-final.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Makoto_Sakuta\" title=\"Makoto Sakuta\">Makoto Sakuta</a>, <a href=\"/Hiroyuki_Iida\" title=\"Hiroyuki Iida\">Hiroyuki Iida</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_4\">Solving Kriegspiel-Like Problems: Examining Efficient Search Methods</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Thomas_Lincke\" title=\"Thomas Lincke\">Thomas Lincke</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_5\">Strategies for the Automatic Construction of Opening Books</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Roel_van_der_Goot&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Roel van der Goot (page does not exist)\">Roel van der Goot</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_6\">Awari Retrograde Analysis</a></i>.</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Haw-ren_Fang\" title=\"Haw-ren Fang\">Haw-ren Fang</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_7\">Construction of Chinese Chess Endgame Databases by Retrograde Analysis</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Learning_and_Pattern_Acquisition\">Learning and Pattern Acquisition</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2000&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Learning and Pattern Acquisition\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jack_van_Rijswijck&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jack van Rijswijck (page does not exist)\">Jack van Rijswijck</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_8\">Learning from Perfection: A Data Mining Approach to Evaluation Function Learning in Awari</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sites.google.com/site/javhar1/LearningFromPerfection.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Robert_Levinson\" title=\"Robert Levinson\">Robert Levinson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ryan_Weber&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ryan Weber (page does not exist)\">Ryan Weber</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_9\">Chess Neighborhoods, Function Combination, and Reinforcement Learning</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://users.soe.ucsc.edu/~levinson/Papers/CNFCRL.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_Ramon&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jan Ramon (page does not exist)\">Jan Ramon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_Francis&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tom Francis (page does not exist)\">Tom Francis</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Hendrik_Blockeel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Hendrik Blockeel (page does not exist)\">Hendrik Blockeel</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=