e Generation Using Move Merit Analysis with Cut-Off Thresholds in Shogi</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jiefu_Shi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jiefu Shi (page does not exist)\">Jiefu Shi</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_L._Littman\" title=\"Michael L. Littman\">Michael L. Littman</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F3-540-45579-5_22\">Abstraction Methods for Game Theoretic Poker</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Takahisa_Ando&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Takahisa Ando (page does not exist)\">Takahisa Ando</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Takao_Uehara&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Takao Uehara (page does not exist)\">Takao Uehara</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_23\">Reasoning by Agents in Computer Bridge Bidding</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Invited_Talks_and_Reviews\">Invited Talks and Reviews</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2000&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Invited Talks and Reviews\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Boris_Stilman\" title=\"Boris Stilman\">Boris Stilman</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_24\">Linguistic Geometry for Solving War Games</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CG 2000</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Kei-ichi_Tainaka&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kei-ichi Tainaka (page does not exist)\">Kei-ichi Tainaka</a> (<b>2000</b>). 